<li><strong><a href="https://sum.vn/tqmu0">Betakkuma &#8220;đầu gấu&#8221;</a></strong></li>
</ul>
<figure id="attachment_88610" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-88610" style="width: 636px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="wp-image-88610 size-full" src="https://img.atpsoftware.vn/2020/01/Sticker-Facebook-ATP-5.png" alt="Betakkuma" width="636" height="960" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-88610" class="wp-caption-text">Betakkuma</figcaption></figure>
